hadiths[45]{hadithnumber,text}:
1460,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki do nishaniyan hain. unhein kisi ki maut aur paidaish ki wajeh sey girahan nahin lagta balke Allah Taala unkey zariey sey apney bandon ko darata hai."
1461,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Madina Munawra mein teer andazi kar raha tha ke suraj ko girahan lag gaya. mainey apney teer ikhattey kiye aur dil mein azm kya ke main zarur ja kar dekhunga ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us moqey par kya tariqa ikhtiyar farmatey hain. main aap ki pichli janib sey aap key qarib aaya. us waqt aap masjid mein they. aap tasbih o takbir padhney lagey aur dua karney lagey yahan tak ke girahan khatam ho gaya, phir aap uthey aur aap ney do rakatein padhein aur chaar sajdey kiye."
1462,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : suraj aur chaand kisi ki maut o hayaat ki wajeh sey be Noor nahin hotey balke ye to Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein sey do nishaniyan hain. jab tum unhein girahan ki haalat mein dekho to namaz padho."
1463,"Hazrat abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : suraj aur chaand kisi ki maut ki bina par be Noor nahin hotey balke ye to Allah Taala ki nishaniyan hain. jab tum unhein (us haal mein) dekho to namaz padho."
1464,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein sey do nishaniyan hain. unhein kisi ki maut o hayaat ki bina par girahan nahin lagta. jab tum unhein girahan ki haalat mein dekho to namaz padho yahan tak ke ye haalat khatam ho jaey."
1465,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas bethey they ke suraj ko girahan lag gaya. aap apna kapda ghaseet-tey huye uthey, phir aap ney do rakatein padhein yahan tak ke suraj saaf roshan ho gaya."
1466,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein suraj ko girahan lag gaya. to aap ney eik aelan karney waley ko hukm diya ke wo ye aelan karey ke namaz (namaz kusuf) key liye jama ho jaeyn. log jama ho gaey aur unhoney saf bandi ki to aap ney unhein do rakatein chaar rukoo aur chaar sajdon key sath padhaain.
1467,Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki biwi mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zindagi mein suraj ko girahan lag gaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) masjid ki taraf nikley. khadey huye aur « Allahu-akbar » kaha. logon ney aap key peechey safein bandhin. is tarah aap ney (do rakaaton mein) chaar rukoo aur chaar sajdey mukammal kiye. aur palatney (farigh honey) sey pehley suraj roshan ho gaya (girahan khatam ho gaya).
1468,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney suraj girahan key waqt aath rukoo aur chaar sajdey kiye. ( yani har rakat mein chaar rukoo kiye.) Hazrat Ata sey bhi usi qism ki riwayat aati hai."
1469,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney girahan key waqt namaz padhi. pehley qirat ki, phir rukoo kya, phir qirat ki, phir rukoo kya, phir qirat ki, phir rukoo kya, phir qirat ki, phir rukoo kya, phir sajda kya, phir dusri rakat bhi isi tarah padhi. ( yani har rakat mein chaar rukoo kiye. )"
1470,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney suraj girahan key din do rakaaton mein chaar rukoo aur chaar sajdey kiye. (yani har rakat mein do rukoo kiye.)
1471,"Hazrat Ata bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Ubaid bin Umer ko kehtey suna ke mujhey us shakhsiyat ney bayan kya jinhein main bilkul sacha samajhta hun. mera khayal hai unka ishara Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf tha. unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein suraj ko girahan lag gaya. aap ney logon ko bada lamba qiyam karwaya. qiyam farmatey they, phir rukoo kartey they, phir qiyam farmatey they, phir rukoo kartey they, phir qiyam farmatey they, phir rukoo farmatey they. aap ney do rakatein padhin har rakat mein teen rukoo they. teesra rukoo karney key baad sajda kya yahan tak ke itney lambey qiyam ki wajeh sey us din kuch logon par ghashi ki haalat taari ho gaee aur un par pani key dol bahaaey gaey. jab aap rukoo ko jatey to « Allahu-akbar » kehtey aur jab apna sar uthatey to « Samiallahu liman hamida » kehtey. aap namaz sey us waqt farigh huye jab suraj bilkul roshan ho gaya. aap ( taqreer key liye) khadey huye. Allah Taala ki hamd o sana ki aur farmaya : suraj aur chaand kisi ki maut o hayaat ki wajeh sey be Noor nahin hotey, balke wo to Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein sey do nishaniyan hain. Allah Taala tumhein unkey zariey sey darata hai, lihaza jab wo be Noor ho jaeyn to khof zada ho kar Allah Taala ka zikr shuru kar do yahan tak ke wo roshan ho jaeyn."
1472,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney chaar sajdon mein ( yani do rakaaton mein) chhe rukoo kiye. ( Hadees key raawi Is-haq kehtey hain ke ) mainey Muaz ( ibn Hisham ) sey kaha : ye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey hai? unhoney kaha : koi shak o shubha nahin.
1473,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki Hayate-Teyeba mein suraj ko girahan lag gaya. aap ( namaz key liye) uthey . « Allahu-akbar » kaha. logon ney bhi aap key peechey safein bandhin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney lambi qirat farmaey, phir « Allahu-akbar » kaha aur lamba rukoo kya, phir apna sar uthaya aur «( سمع اللہ لمن حمدہ ربنا ولک الحمد ) kaha, phir qiyam shuru kar diya aur lambi qirat ki jo ke pehli qirat sey kam thi, phir « Allahu-akbar » kaha aur lamba rukoo kya jo pehley rukoo sey kam tha, phir ( سمع اللہ لمن حمدہ ربنا ولک الحمد ) kaha, phir sajda kya, phir dusri rakat mein bhi isi tarah kya. aur chaar rukoo aur chaar sajdey mukammal kiye. aap key ( namaz sey) farigh honey sey pehley suraj mukammal roshan ho chuka tha, phir aap khadey huye aur logon ko khutba diya. Allah Taala ki hamd o sana ki jis ka wo ehal hai, phir farmaya : suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein sey do nishaniyan hain. unhein kisi ki maut o hayaat ki wajeh sey girahan nahin lagta. jab tum unhein (girahan laga huwa) dekho to namaz kusuf shuru kar do yahan tak ke girahan ki haalat khatam ho jaey. neez Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey us (namaz key) qiyam key doran mein har chiz dekh li jiska tum sey wada kya gaya hai. jab tum ney mujhey aagey badhtey huye dekha tha to darasal mainey jannat sey eik khosha todney ka irada kya tha. aur jab tum ney mujhey peechey hattey huye dekha tha to darasal mainey jahannam ko dekha tha ke uskey mukhtalif hissey eik dusrey ko tod rahey they, neez mainey jahannam mein Amr bin Luhi ko dekha aur ye wo shakhs hai jisney buton key naam par janwer khuley chhodney ki rasm dali."
1474,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein suraj ko girahan lag gaya to aelan kya gaya : namaz ki jamaat honi hai. log ikhattey ho gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein namaz padhaai. aur ( do rakaaton mein) chaar rukoo aur chaar sajdey kiye.
1475,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein suraj ko girahan lag gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney logon ko namaz kusoof padhaai. aap ney qiyam farmaya aur bahut lamba qiyam farmaya, phir rukoo farmaya aur bahut lamba rukoo farmaya, phir qiyam farmaya aur lamba qiyam farmaya lekin ye pehley qiyam sey kam tha, phir rukoo farmaya aur lamba rukoo farmaya lekin ye pehley rukoo sey kam tha, phir sar uthaya, phir sajda kya, phir dusri rakat mein bhi aisey hi kya, phir farigh huye to suraj puri tarah roshan ho chuka tha, phir aap ney logon ko khutba diya. Allah ki hamd o sanaa ki, phir farmaya : bilashuba suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein sey do nishaniyan hain. unhein kisi ki maut o hayaat ki wajeh sey girahan nahin lagta . jab tum ye soorate-hal dekho to Allah Taala sey duayen karo aur Allah Taala ki buzurgi bayan karo aur sadqaat karo. phir farmaya : aey ummat Muhammad ! koi shakhs Allah Taala sey badh kar us baat par ghairat nahin karta ke us ka koi ghulam ya londi zina kerey. aey ummat Muhammad ! Allah ki qism ! agar tum wo cheezen jaan lo jo main janta hun to tum bahut kam hanso aur bahut ziyada ro-o."
1476,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke eik Yahudi aurat merey paas aai aur kehney lagi : Allah Taala tujhey qabr key azab sey bachaey. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya logon ko qabron mein azab hoga ? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main Allah ki panah mein aata hun. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik dafa nikley. itney mein suraj ko girahan lag gaya. hum sab hujrey mein chaley aaye. hamarey paas bahut si aurten ikhatti ho gaeen. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi tashrif ley aaye. ye chaasht ( din chadhney ) key waqt ki baat hai, phir aap ney lamba qiyam farmaya, phir lamba rukoo farmaya, phir sar utha kar dobara qiyam kya lekin ye pehley qiyam sey kam tha, phir pehley rukoo sey kam rukoo kya, phir sajda kya, phir dusri rakat key liye khadey huye aur is mein bhi isi tarah kya magar us rakat key qiyam o rukoo pehli rakat key muqabley mein kam they, phir sajdey kiye aur suraj bhi pura roshan ho gaya. jab aap namaz sey farigh huye to member par beth gaey aur ( taqreer key doran mein) farmaya : bilashuba logon ko qabron mein fitna dajjaal ki tarah aazmaya jaeyga. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke uskey baad hum aap ko aksar azab qabr sey panah maangtey suntey they."
1477,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik Yahudi aurat merey paas kuch maangney aai. wo kehney lagi : Allah Taala tujhey azab qabr sey bachaey . jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya logon ko qabron mein azab diya jaeyga ? aap ney farmaya : main Allah ki panah chahta hun. phir aap sawari par sawar ho kar kahin gaey. udhar suraj ko girahan lag gaya. main dusri aurton key sath hujron key darmiyan khadi thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sawari sey utar kar tashrif laye apni namaz ki jagah mein pahunchey, phir logon ko namaz padhana shuru ki, chunanche aap ney qiyam kya aur bahut lamba qiyam kya, phir rukoo kya aur lamba rukoo kya, phir apna sar uthaya aur lamba qiyam kya, phir rukoo kya aur lamba rukoo kya, phir apna sar uthaya aur der tak khadey rahey, phir sajda kya aur lamba sajda kya, phir (dusrey sajdey key baad) khadey huye aur pehley qiyam sey halka qiyam kya, phir pehley rukoo sey halka rukoo kya, phir apna sar uthaya aur pehley qiyam sey halka qiyam kya, phir apney pehley rukoo sey halka rukoo kya, phir sar uthaya aur pehley sey kuch kam der khadey rahey is tarah chaar rukoo aur chaar sajdey huye. udhar suraj bhi roshan ho gaya, phir aap ney ( khutba key doran mein) farmaya : tumhein qabron mein fitna dajjaal ki tarah aazmaya jaeyga. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain : uskey baad mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko azab qabr sey panah maangtey suna."
1478,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney suraj girahan key moqey par zam zam key chabootrey par namaz padhi, is mein chaar rukoo kiye aur chaar sajdey kiye."
1479,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney main eik sakht garm din mein suraj girahan laga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney sahaba ko namaz kusoof padhaai. aap ney bahut lamba qiyam farmaya yahan tak ke log girney lagey, phir aap ney rukoo farmaya aur lamba rukoo farmaya, phir aap ney sar uthaya to lamba qiyam farmaya, phir rukoo farmaya aur lamba rukoo farmaya, phir sar uthaya to kafi der khadey rahey, phir do sajdey kiye. phir khadey huye aur dusri rakat bhi isi tarah padhi. ( qiyam key doran mein) aap aagey badhtey they, phir peechey hat-tey they. to is tarah ye chaar rukoo aur chaar sajdey huye. log kaha kartey they ke suraj aur chaand ko kisi azeem sardar ki wafat par hi girahan lagta hai. (aap ney farmaya : ) ye dono Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein sey do nishaniyan hain jo Allah Taala tumhein dikhata hai. to jab un mein sey kisi ko girahan lag jaey to namaz padho yahan tak ke wo roshan ho jaey."
1480,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein suraj ko girahan lag gaya. aap key hukm sey aelan kya gaya ke namaz ki jamaat honi hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney logon ko do rukoo key sath eik rakat padhaai, phir aap khadey huye aur do rukoo key sath eik aur rakat padhi. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke us sey ziyada lamba rukoo aur sajda mainey kabhi nahin kya. Muhammad bin Himyar ney (us riwayat key bayan mein) Marwan ki mukhalifat ki hai."
1481,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke eik dafa suraj ko girahan lag gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ( pehli rakat mein) do rukoo aur do sajdey farmaey. phir aap khadey huye aur (dusri rakat mein bhi ) do rukoo aur do sajdey farmaey. itney mein suraj roshan ho gaya. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmaya karti thin : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey lamba rukoo aur sajda kabhi nahin kya. Ali bin mubarak ney Muawiya bin salam ki mukhalifat ki hai.
1482,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) batati hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein suraj ko girahan laga to aap ney wuzu farmaya aur hukm diya to aelan kya gaya ke namaz ki jamaat honi hai, phir aap ney qiyam shuru farmaya aur namaz mein bahut lamba qiyam farmaya. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : mera andaza hai ke aap ney Sura Baqra padhi, phir aap ney rukoo farmaya aur lamba rukoo farmaya, phir farmaya : « Samiallahu liman hamida » , phir qiyam kya jis tarah pehla qiyam farmaya tha. sajda nahin kya, phir rukoo mein gaey, phir sajda kya, phir khadey huye aur us rakat mein bhi pehli rakat ki tarah do rukoo aur do sajdey kiye, phir ( tashahud mein) bethey . itney mein suraj bhi roshan ho gaya."
1483,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein suraj ko girahan lag gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz key liye uthey. jo log aap key sath they, wo bhi uthey. aap ney qiyam farmaya aur bada lamba qiyam farmaya, phir rukoo farmaya to bahut lamba rukoo farmaya, phir apna sar uthaya aur sajda farmaya aur bahut lamba sajda farmaya, phir sar uthaya aur beth gaey. bahut der bethey rahey, phir doosra sajda kiya aur bahut lamba sajda kiya, phir sar uthaya aur khadey ho gaey, phir dusri rakat mein bhi isi tarah qiyam, rukoo, sajda aur jalsa kiya jis tarah pehli rakat mein kiya tha. dusri rakat key aakhiri sajdey mein aap aahen bharney aur roney lagey. aap farmatey they : aey Allah ! tera mujh sey wada hai ke jab tak to inkey andar mojud hai, main azab nahin bhejunga. aey Allah ! tera mujh sey wada hai ke jab tak hum tujh sey bakhshish talab kartey rahengey, to azab nazil nahin kerega. phir aap ney sar uthaya to suraj roshan ho chuka tha, phir Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uthey aur logon sey khitab farmaya. pehley Allah Taala ki hamd aur sanaa bayan farmaee. phir farmaya : bilashuba suraj aur chaand Allah ki nishaniyon mein sey do nishaniyan hain. jab tum un mein sey kisi ka girahan dekho to jaldi sey Allah Taala key zikr ki taraf chalo. qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! jannat merey itni qarib ki gaee ke agar main apna haath badhata to uskey (phalon key) kuchh khoshey tod leta. aur aag merey is qadr qarib ki gaee ke main us sey bachney laga. mujhey khatra mehsus honey laga tha ke kahin wo tum par na chha jaey, isi ke sath mainey is mein bnu Himyar ki eik aurat dekhi jisey eik billi ki wajeh sey azab diya ja raha tha jisey us ney baandhey rakha. na to usey chhoda ke wo zamin key keedey makodey khati aur na usey khud khilaya pilaya, yahan tak ke wo (billi bhook piyas sey) mar gaee. Allah ki qism ! mainey usey (billi ko) dekha ke wo aurat jab uski taraf munh karti thi to wo usey nochti thi aur jab wo peeth karti thi to uskey sareen (peeth) ko kaatti thi. aur yahan tak ke mainey aag mein banu Da'daa key eik joota chor ko dekha jisey eik do-shaakh wali lakdi key sath aag mein dhakela ja raha tha. aur mainey aag mein us chhadi waley ko dekha jo apni chhadi sey hajiyon ka saman churaayaa karta tha. wo aag mein apni chhadi key saharey khada keh raha tha. (aey logo ! ) main hun chhadi sey chori karney wala."
1484,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein suraj gahanaa gaya. aap uthey aur logon ko namaz padhaai. lamba qiyam kiya, phir rukoo kiya aur lamba rukoo kiya, phir khadey huye aur lamba qiyam kiya lekin ye pehley qiyam sey kam tha, phir rukoo farmaya aur lamba rukoo farmaya magar ye pehley rukoo sey kam tha, phir sajda kiya aur lamba sajda kiya, phir sar uthaya, phir doosra sajda kiya aur lamba sajda kiya lekin ye pehley sajdey sey kam tha, phir khadey huye aur do rukoo kiye. dono mein aisey hi kiya, phir do sajdey kiye. dono mein aisey hi kiya, yahan tak ke namaz sey farigh ho gaey, phir farmaya : yaqinan suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein sey do nishaniyan hain aur ye kisi ki maut aur hayaat ki wajeh sey nahin gahnaatey. jab tum un ki ye haalat dekho to fauran Allah Taala ka zikr aur namaz shuru kar do."
1485,"Hazrat Saulba bin Ibaad Abdi sey riwayat hai. . ۔ wo Basra key rehney waley they. . ۔ unhoney eik dafa Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey khutba suna. unhoney apney khutbey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey eik hadees bayan farmaee. farmaya : eik din main aur Ansaar ka eik ladka Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein (apney muqarrar karda nishaanon par) teer andazi kar rahey they. jab suraj dekhney waley ki nazar mein ufaq sey do teen neze ooncha aa gaya to be-Noor ho gaya. hum mein sey eik ney dusrey sey kaha : aao masjid chalen. Allah ki qism ! suraj ki ye haalat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye aap ki ummat mein kisi naey hukm ka sabab baneygi. hum masjid ki taraf chaley to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamein logon ki taraf nikaltey huye miley. aap aagey badhey aur namaz shuru kar di. aap ney itna lamba qiyam farmaya ke kabhi kisi namaz mein itna lamba qiyam nahin farmaya. hum aap ki aawaz nahin suntey they, phir aap ney hamarey sath rukoo kiya aur itna lamba rukoo ke kabhi kisi namaz mein itna lamba rukoo nahin kiya tha. hum aap ki aawaz nahin suntey they, phir aap ney hamarey sath sajda kiya. itna lamba sajda ke kabhi kisi namaz mein itna lamba sajda nahin kiya tha. hum aap ki aawaz nahin suntey they, phir aap ney dusri rakat mein bhi aisey hi kiya. jab aap dusri rakat key aakhir mein bethey to suraj roshan ho chuka tha. aap ney salam phera, phir Allah ki hamd aur sanaa ki aur is baat ki shahadat di ke Allah key siwa koi (haqeeqi aur sachcha) mabood nahin aur is baat ki shahadat di ke wo (aap) Allah key bandey aur uskey bhejey huye (Rasool) hain. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai."
1486,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein suraj gahanaa gaya. aap ghabra kar apna kapda (baalaai chadar) ghaseet'tey huye ghar sey nikley yahan tak ke masjid mein aaye aur hamein namaz padhaai yahan tak ke suraj saaf ho gaya. jab suraj saaf ho gaya to farmaya : log kehtey hain ke suraj aur chaand kisi badey sardar ki maut hi par gahnaatey hain, halanke ye haqiqat nahin. suraj aur chaand kisi ki maut aur hayaat ki wajeh sey nahin gahnaatey balke ye to Allah Taala ki (azmat aur tohid ki) nishaniyon mein sey do nishaniyan hain. jab Allah apni kisi makhluq par tajalli farmata hai to wo makhluq fauran uski itaat karti hai. jab tum ye soorate-haal dekho to is qarib-tareen farz namaz ki tarah namaz padho jo tum ney (ab sey pehley) padhi hai, (yani Fajr ki tarah)."
1487,"Hazrat Qabeesa bin Makhaariq Hilaali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Madiney mein they ke suraj gahanaa gaya. aap ghabra kar apna kapda ghaseet'tey huye nikley, phir aap ney do rakatein padhin aur khub lambi padhin idhar aap namaz sey farigh huye, udhar suraj bhi roshan ho gaya. aap ney Allah Taala ki hamd aur sanaa bayan ki, phir farmaya : suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein sey do nishaniyan hain aur unhein kisi ki maut aur hayaat ki bina par girahan nahin lagta. jab tum is qisam ki koi chiz dekho to is qarib tareen farz namaz ki tarah namaz padho jo tum ney padhi hai."
1488,"Hazrat Qabeesa Hilaali (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik dafa suraj gahanaa gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney do rakatein padhin yahan tak ke suraj roshan ho gaya, phir aap ney farmaya : bilashuba suraj aur chaand kisi ki maut ki bina par nahin gahnaatey balke wo Allah Taala ki makhluqat mein sey do makhluq hain aur Allah Taala apni makhluq mein jo chahey tabdili lata hai aur Allah Taala jab apni kisi makhluq par tajalli farmata hai to wo fauran uski itaat karti hai. to jab un dono mein sey kisi mein koi tabdili waqey ho (suraj ya chaand ko girahan lagey) to namaz padho yahan tak ke wo roshan ho jaey ya Allah Taala koi aur Amr (bat) sadir (laagu) farma dey."
1489,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab suraj ya chaand ko girahan lag jaey to us qarib tareen namaz ki tarah namaz padho jo tum ney padhi hai,  yani Fajr ki namaz)."
1490,Hazrat Noman bin Bashir Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke jab suraj ko girahan laga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamari namaz ki tarah namaz padhi. aap rukoo aur sajda kartey they.
1491,"Hazrat Noman bin Basheer Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke eik din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) masjid ki taraf tezi sey nikley kyonkey suraj ko girahan lag gaya tha. aap namaz padhtey rahey yahan tak ke suraj roshan ho gaya. phir aap ney farmaya : jahiliyat waley log kehtey they ke suraj aur chaand ko kisi badey zamini sardar ki maut ki wajeh sey girahan lagta hai, jabkey haqiqat ye hai ke suraj aur chaand ko kisi ki maut aur hayaat ki wajeh sey girahan nahin lagta balke ye dono to Allah Taala ki makhluqat mein sey do makhluqeyn hain. Allah Taala apni makhluq mein jo chahey tabdili la sakta hai, lihaza un mein sey kisi ko girahan lag jaey to namaz padho yahan tak ke wo roshan ho jaey ya Allah Taala koi nayi baat jari farma dey."
1492,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas they ke suraj ko girahan lag gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni baalaai chadar ko ghaseet'tey huye nikley yahan tak ke masjid mein pahunchey. log bhi aap key paas jama ho gaey. aap ney hamein do rakatein padhaain. jab girahan khatam ho gaya to aap ney farmaya : suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki do nishaniyan hain. Allah Taala un (key girahan) key zariey sey apney bandon ko darata hai. unhein kisi ki maut aur hayaat ki bina par girahan nahin lagta, chunanche jab tum aisi soorate-haal dekho to namaz shuru kar do yahan tak ke girahan khatam ho jaey. ye aap ney, is liye irshad farmaya ke us din aap ka beta (Hazrat Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu)) faut ho gaya tha to logon ney is barey mein ye kehna shuru kar diya tha (ke girahan un ki wafat ki wajeh sey laga hai)."
1493,Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tumhari is namaz (namaze-kusoof) ki tarah do rakatein padhi thin aur unhoney suraj girahan ka zikr kiya tha.
1494,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke suraj ko girahan lag gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz padhi jabkey log bhi aap key sath (namaz mein shamil) they. aap ney lamba qiyam farmaya aur Sura Baqra key barabar qirat ki, phir aap ney lamba rukoo farmaya, phir sar uthaya aur lamba qiyam kiya jabkey ye pehley qiyam sey kam tha, phir lamba rukoo kiya aur ye pehley rukoo sey kam tha, phir sajdey kiye, phir lamba qiyam kiya aur ye pehley qiyam sey kam tha, phir lamba rukoo farmaya aur ye pehley rukoo sey kam tha, phir sar uthaya aur lamba qiyam farmaya magar ye pehley qiyam sey kam tha, phir lamba rukoo farmaya magar ye pehley rukoo sey kam tha, phir sajdey kiye, phir salam pheraa. us waqt tak suraj roshan ho chuka tha, phir aap ney farmaya : bilashuba suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki do nishaniyan hain. unhein kisi ki maut aur hayaat ki wajeh sey girahan nahin lagta, lihaza jab tum ye soorate-haal dekho to Allah ko yad kiya karo. logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamney aap ko dekha tha ke aap ney apney qiyam key doran mein kisi chiz ko pakadney ki koshish ki, phir hamney dekha ke aap peechhey hatey? aap ney farmaya : mainey jannat dekhi. ya farmaya : mujhey jannat dikhaai gaee to mainey us sey eik khosha leney ki koshish ki thi aur agar main usey ley leta to tum rehti duniya tak us sey khatey rehtey, isi ke sath mainey aag dekhi. mainey us jaisa khof naak manzar kabhi nahin dekha aur mainey jahannam mein ziyada aurton ko dekha. logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kyon? aap ney farmaya : apney kufr ki wajeh sey. kaha gaya : wo Allah key sath kufr karti hain? aap ney farmaya : nahin, wo khawind ki nashukri karti hain aur ehsan-faramosh hain. agar to un mein sey kisi key sath sari zindagi husne-sulook kerey. phir wo tujh sey koi nagawar chiz dekhey to kahegi : mainey tujh sey kabhi koi achchhaa sulook nahin dekha."
1495,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney chaar sajdon (yani do rakaaton) main chaar rukoo kiye. aur namaze kusoof mein buland aawaz sey qirat farmaee. jab bhi rukoo sey sar uthatey they to kehtey : ( Samiallahu-liman-hamida) (ربنا ولک الحمد).
1496,Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein namaze kusoof padhaai. hum aap ki aawaz nahin suntey they.
1497,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein suraj ko girahan lag gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz padhi. qiyam bahut lamba kiya, phir rukoo kiya to lamba rukoo kiya, phir sar uthaya to bahut der khadey rahey. isi tarah sajda bhi khub lamba kiya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sajdey mein rotey they, aahen bhartey they aur farmatey they : aey merey Rab ! tu ney mujh sey is (azab) ka wada nahin kiya tha jabkey main to tujh sey bakhshish talab kar raha hun. tu ney mujh sey is (azab) ka wada nahin kiya tha jabkey main in mein mojud hun. jab aap namaz sey farigh huye to farmaya : mujh par jannat pesh ki gaee, yahan tak ke agar main apna haath badhata to main uskey kuchh khoshey ley leta, isi ke sath mujh par aag pesh ki gaee to main is mein phunkeyn maarney laga ke kahin tumhein uski tapish na aa ley. aur mainey is mein apni do oontniyon ka chor bhi dekha, isi ke sath mainey is mein banu Da'daa ka wo shakhs dekha jo hajiyon ki cheezen churaayaa karta tha. aur agar pata chal jata to wo kehta ke ye chhadi ki kaaristaani hai. aur mainey us main eik lambi kaali aurat dekhi jisey eik billi key barey mein azab diya ja raha tha jisey us ney baandh diya tha. na to usey khilaya pilaya aur na usey chhoda ke wo khud zamin key keedey makodey kha leti yahan tak ke wo mar gaee. aur (yaad rakho !) suraj aur chaand kisi ki maut aur hayaat ki wajeh sey nahin gahnaatey, balke ye Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein sey do nishaniyan hain. jab un mein sey kisi ko girahan lag jaey to Allah Taala key zikr ki taraf daudo."
1498,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke eik dafa suraj ko girahan lag gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko hukm diya to usney aelan kiya ke namaz ki jamaat honey wali hai. log ikhattey ho gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein namaz padhaai. aap ney (Allahu-Akbar) kaha, phir lambi qirat ki, phir (Allahu-Akbar) kaha aur lamba rukoo kiya, apney qiyam jitna ya us sey bhi lamba, phir apna sar uthaya aur (Samiallahu-liman-hamida) kaha, phir taweel qirat ki jo pehli qirat sey kam thi, phir (Allahu-Akbar) kaha aur lamba rukoo kiya jo pehley rukoo sey kam tha. phir sar uthaya aur (Samiallahu liman hamida) kaha, phir (Allahu-Akbar) kaha aur lamba sajda kiya, rukoo jitna ya us sey bhi lamba, phir (Allahu-Akbar) keh kar sar uthaya aur phir (Allahu-Akbar) keh kar sajda kiya, phir (Allahu-Akbar) keh kar uthey aur lambi qirat ki jo pehli qirat sey kam thi, phir (Allahu-Akbar) kaha aur lamba rukoo kiya jo pehley rukoo sey kam tha, phir sar uthaya aur (Samiallahu liman hamida) kaha aur phir lambi qirat ki jo dusrey qiyam ki pehli qirat sey kam thi, phir (Allahu-Akbar) kaha aur lamba lekin pehley rukoo sey kam lamba rukoo kiya, phir uthaya aur (Samiallahu liman hamida) kaha, phir (Allahu-Akbar) keh kar pehley sajdon sey kam lambey sajdey kiye. phir tashahud padha, phir salam pheraa. phir aap (taqreer key liye) khadey huye. Allah Taala ki hamd aur sanaa ki, phir farmaya : suraj aur chaand kisi ki maut aur hayaat ki bina par be-Noor nahin hotey balke ye to Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein sey do nishaniyan hain. un mein sey jisey girahan lag jaey to ghabra kar (fauran) namaz ki surat mein Allah ka zikr shuru kar do."
1499,"Hazrat Asma binte Abi Bakar Raziallahu anhuma farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney suraj girahan mein namaz padhi. qiyam kiya aur bahut lamba qiyam kiya, phir rukoo kiya aur bahut lamba rukoo kiya, phir sar uthaya aur lamba qiyam kiya, phir rukoo kiya aur lamba rukoo kiya, phir sar uthaya, phir sajda kiya aur lamba sajda kiya, phir sar uthaya, phir sajda kiya aur lamba sajda kiya, phir khadey huye aur lamba qiyam kiya, phir rukoo kiya aur lamba rukoo kiya, phir sar uthaya aur lamba qiyam kiya, phir rukoo kiya aur lamba rukoo kiya, phir sar uthaya, phir sajda kiya aur lamba sajda kiya, phir sar uthaya, phir sajda kiya aur lamba sajda kiya, phir sar uthaya (aur tashahud aur durood waghera padha). phir salam pheraa."
1500,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kisi kaam sey nikley they ke suraj be-Noor ho gaya. hum hujrey ki taraf chaley aaye. dusri aurten bhi hamarey paas ikhatti ho gaeen. itney mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi hamari taraf tashrif ley aaye. ye chaasht ka waqt tha. aap ney lamba qiyam farmaya, phir lamba rukoo farmaya, phir sar utha kar pehley qiyam sey kam lamba qiyam kiya, phir pehley rukoo sey kam lamba rukoo kiya, phir sajdey kiye, phir dusri rakat key liye khadey huye aur isi tarah kiya, magar aap key qiyam aur rukoo pehli rakat sey kam lambey they, phir aap ney sajdey kiye. udhar suraj bhi roshan ho gaya. jab salam pheraa to member par tashrif farma huye (aur bahut si baaten irshad farmaeen). in mein ye bhi farmaya : bilashuba log qabron mein fitna Dajjaal ki tarah aazamaye jaeyngey. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai."
1501,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein suraj ko girahan lag gaya. aap khadey huye aur namaz shuru kar di to bahut hi lamba qiyam farmaya, phir rukoo farmaya to bahut hi lamba rukoo farmaya, phir sar uthaya to bahut lamba qiyam farmaya magar ye pehley qiyam sey kam lamba tha, phir doosra rukoo farmaya aur lamba rukoo farmaya magar ye pehley rukoo sey kam lamba tha, phir sajda farmaya (do dafa), phir sar uthaya aur lamba qiyam kiya jo pehley qiyam sey kam lamba tha aur phir rukoo farmaya aur lamba rukoo farmaya jo pehley rukoo sey kam lamba tha, phir sar uthaya aur lamba qiyam farmaya jo pehley qiyam sey kam lamba tha, phir rukoo farmaya aur lamba rukoo farmaya jo pehley rukoo sey kam lamba tha, phir sajdey farmaai aur namaz sey farigh huye to girahan khatam ho chuka tha, phir aap ney logon sey khitab farmaya. Allah Taala ki hamd aur sanaa bayan farmaee, phir farmaya : suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki azmat ki do nishaniyan hain. ye kisi ki maut aur hayaat ki bina par be-noor nahin hotey, lihaza jab tum ye haalat dekho to namaz padho, sadqaat karo aur Allah Taala ko yad karo. aur farmaya : aey ummate Muhammad ! kisi ko Allah Taala sey badh kar ghairat nahin aati is baat par ke us ka ghulam ya laundi zina kerey. aey ummate Muhammad ! agar tum wo baaten jaan lo jo main janta hun to tum kam hanso aur ziyada rau'o."
1502,Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jab suraj ko girahan laga tha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khutba diya tha aur farmaya tha : (Ammaa baad !).
1503,Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath they ke suraj ko girahan lag gaya. aap jaldi sey apni baalaai chadar ghaseet'tey huye masjid ki taraf chaley log bhi aap key paas aa gaey. aap ney do rakat namaz padhaai jaisey wo (ehale Madina namaze kusoof) padhtey they. jab suraj roshan ho gaya to aap ney hamein khutba diya aur farmaya : bilashuba suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein sey do nishaniyan hain. Allah Taala unkey zariey sey apney bandon ko darata hai aur unhein kisi ki maut ki bina par girahan nahin lagta. jab tum un mein sey kisi ko girahan lagta dekho to namaz padho aur duayen karo yahan tak ke girahan khatam ho jaey.
1504,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik dafa suraj gahanaa gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ghabra kar uthey. aap ko khatra huwa ke qiyamat na aa jaey. aap uthey yahan tak ke masjid mein aaye aur khadey ho kar itney lambey qiyam, rukoo aur sajdey key sath namaz padhi ke mainey kabhi aap ko kisi namaz mein itney lambey qiyam, rukoo aur sajdey kartey nahin dekha, phir aap ney farmaya : tehqiq ye nishaniyan jo Allah Taala zahir farmata hai, kisi ki maut aur hayaat ki bina par nahin hoten balke Allah Taala unhein ,is liye zahir farmata hai ke apney bandon key dilon mein un ki bina par apna khof paida farmaey. jab tum koi aisi chiz dekho to fauran Allah ka zikr karo, duayen karo aur us sey apney gunahon ki bakhshish talab karo."
